From: robert-brunson-fragile <siinspam@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:20:47 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 4/8] feat(image-gen): add Civitai local subprocess image
 generation provider

Add a Civitai Orchestration API image-gen provider that runs in a clean
subprocess (Cloudflare blocks Python TLS/proxy-routed traffic from the
agent host). The subprocess strips proxy env vars and connects directly.

  - plugins/image_gen/civitai/: provider + plugin.yaml manifest
  - agent/image_gen_provider.py: add prefer_local_execution flag to the
    base ImageGenProvider so dispatch can route to subprocess execution
  - tools/image_generation_tool.py: add the local-execution subprocess
    branch and image-to-image (image_url / reference_image_urls) kwargs
    with a graceful TypeError fallback for providers that lack the new
    signature

Co-authored-by: Nako <280596805+nakoagent@users.noreply.github.com>

